  .popup_oh_no_txt{:style=>"margin: 92px 0 0 3px;"} Oh No!
  .popup_content_txt{:style=>"margin: 20px 0 0 15px;"}
    Apologies, but it appears as though your membership code is no longer valid.
    But fear not, 
    %a{:href => "#{hunt_membership_path}"} 
      %FONT{:COLOR => "red"} find a new code  
    here and let's resume.  Shall we?

